&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Design, implement, and integrate embedded control algorithms for electric powertrain and vehicle systems using model-based development tools (MATLAB/Simulink/Stateflow).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Develop and execute system-level tests on HIL benches, simulators, and actual vehicles to validate control logic, and software performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Support vehicle commissioning, end-of-line testing, and troubleshooting activities at Xos manufacturing facilities and customer locations, including diagnostics and root cause analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Create comprehensive documentation for control software design, implementation, and testing to meet internal standards and regulatory requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Review and assess the impact of software changes, participating in design and requirement reviews to ensure system-level consistency and reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Support change control, version control, and requirements traceability in accordance with internal processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Provide technical feedback to support improvement tools, procedures, and software development standards.&lt;/li&gt;
